@startuml uc6_export_part_3
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title UC-06 Part 3: User Notification và File Download

participant "RabbitMQ\n(notifications)" as MQ
participant "WebSocket Service\n(Golang)" as WS
participant "Redis Pub/Sub" as Redis
actor "Marketing\nAnalyst" as User
participant "Web UI\n(Next.js)" as UI
participant "Project Service\n(Golang)" as ProjectSvc
database "PostgreSQL\n(export_requests)" as DB
participant "MinIO\n(Object Storage)" as MinIO

== Real-time Notification (User Online) ==

MQ -> WS: CONSUME export.completed event\n{\n  "export_request_id": "uuid",\n  "project_id": "uuid",\n  "user_id": "uuid",\n  "download_url": "...",\n  "format": "pdf"\n}
activate WS

WS -> Redis: PUBLISH to channel: user:{user_id}\nMessage:\n{\n  "type": "export_completed",\n  "export_request_id": "uuid",\n  "project_id": "uuid",\n  "format": "pdf"\n}
activate Redis

Redis --> WS: Broadcast to subscribers
deactivate Redis

WS -> WS: Check if user connected\nvia WebSocket

alt User is online (WebSocket connected)

    WS -> UI: Send WebSocket message:\n{\n  "type": "export_completed",\n  "message": "Báo cáo của bạn đã sẵn sàng",\n  "export_request_id": "uuid",\n  "project_id": "uuid"\n}
    activate UI

    UI -> UI: Show notification banner:\n"Báo cáo của bạn đã sẵn sàng"\nwith "Download" button

    UI --> User: Display notification
    deactivate UI

else User is offline

    note over WS, UI
      Notification stored in database
      for later retrieval when user logs in
    end note

end

deactivate WS

== User Downloads File ==

User -> UI: Click "Download" button\n(or navigate to Export History)
activate UI

UI -> ProjectSvc: GET /api/v1/projects/:project_id/exports/:export_id\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>
activate ProjectSvc

ProjectSvc -> ProjectSvc: Verify JWT\nExtract user_id

ProjectSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM export_requests\nWHERE id = :export_id\n  AND project_id = :project_id
activate DB

DB --> ProjectSvc: Return export_request:\n{\n  "id": "uuid",\n  "status": "completed",\n  "download_url": "...",\n  "file_size": 2621440,\n  "format": "pdf",\n  "completed_at": "2025-12-21T11:00:00Z"\n}
deactivate DB

ProjectSvc -> ProjectSvc: Verify ownership:\nproject.created_by == user_id

ProjectSvc -> ProjectSvc: Check URL not expired:\nNOW() < completed_at + 7 days

ProjectSvc --> UI: 200 OK\n{\n  "download_url": "https://minio.../...",\n  "filename": "Brand_A_Analysis_2025-12-21.pdf",\n  "file_size": 2621440,\n  "expires_at": "2025-12-28T11:00:00Z"\n}
deactivate ProjectSvc

== Browser Download ==

UI -> UI: Trigger browser download:\nwindow.location.href = download_url

UI -> MinIO: GET download_url\n(Pre-signed URL with auth params)
activate MinIO

MinIO -> MinIO: Validate signature\nCheck expiry

MinIO --> UI: 200 OK\nContent-Type: application/pdf\nContent-Disposition: attachment;\n  filename="Brand_A_Analysis_2025-12-21.pdf"\n\n[Binary file content: 2.5 MB]
deactivate MinIO

UI -> UI: Browser saves file to\nuser's Downloads folder

UI --> User: File downloaded:\nBrand_A_Analysis_2025-12-21.pdf
deactivate UI

note over User
  User can now open the report
  with PDF viewer, Excel, or text editor
  depending on selected format
end note

== Alternative: Export History Page ==

User -> UI: Navigate to "/exports"\n(Export History page)
activate UI

UI -> ProjectSvc: GET /api/v1/projects/:project_id/exports
activate ProjectSvc

ProjectSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM export_requests\nWHERE project_id = :project_id\n  AND user_id = :user_id\nORDER BY created_at DESC\nLIMIT 20
activate DB

DB --> ProjectSvc: Return list of exports
deactivate DB

ProjectSvc --> UI: 200 OK\n[\n  {id, format, status, file_size,\n   created_at, download_url},\n  ...\n]
deactivate ProjectSvc

UI --> User: Display exports table:\n- Format | Status | Date | Size | Actions
deactivate UI

User -> UI: Click "Download" on specific export

note over UI
  Same download flow as above
end note

== Exception: URL Expired ==

alt Download URL expired (> 7 days)

    ProjectSvc --> UI: 410 Gone\n{\n  "error": "Download URL expired",\n  "message": "Please generate a new export"\n}

    UI --> User: Show error message:\n"Link đã hết hạn, vui lòng xuất báo cáo mới"

end

@enduml
